trans-unit.source: The SearchResult class encapsulates a node in the Active Directory Domain Services hierarchy that is returned during a search through <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SearchResult kapslar in en nod i Active Directory Domain Services-hierarkin som returneras när en sökning via <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Instances of the SearchResult class are very similar to instances of <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class.
trans-unit.target: Instanser av klassen SearchResult liknar instanser av <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>klassen.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>

trans-unit.source: The crucial difference is that the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class retrieves its information from the Active Directory Domain Services hierarchy each time a new object is accessed, whereas the data for SearchResult is already available in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection>, where it gets returned from a query that is performed with the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher> class.
trans-unit.target: Avgörande skillnaden är att <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>klassen hämtar informationen från Active Directory Domain Services hierarkin varje gång som ett nytt objekt används medan data för SearchResult finns redan i <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection>där det returneras från en fråga som utförs med <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher>klass.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>

trans-unit.source: Only those properties that are specified through the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.PropertiesToLoad%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection in your query will be available from SearchResult.
trans-unit.target: Endast de egenskaper som anges via den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.PropertiesToLoad%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samling i frågan ska vara tillgänglig från SearchResult.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.PropertiesToLoad%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> that corresponds to the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult"></xref> from the Active Directory Domain Services hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> som motsvarar den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult"> </xref> från Active Directory Domain Services-hierarkin.

trans-unit.source: Use GetDirectoryEntry when you want to look at the live entry instead of the entry that was returned through <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher>, or when you want to invoke a method on the object that was returned.
trans-unit.target: Använd GetDirectoryEntry när du vill titta på live posten i stället för den post som returnerades genom <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher>, eller när du vill anropa en metod i objektet som returnerades.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Calling GetDirectoryEntry on each <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> returned through <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher> can be slow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Anropar GetDirectoryEntry på varje <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult>returnerade via <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher>kan gå långsamt.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult>

trans-unit.source: The Path property uniquely identifies this entry in the Active Directory Domain Services hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Path identifierar den här posten i Active Directory Domain Services-hierarkin.

trans-unit.source: The entry can always be retrieved using this path.
trans-unit.target: Posten kan alltid hämtas med hjälp av den här sökvägen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyCollection"></xref> collection of properties for this object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyCollection"> </xref> egenskaper för det här objektet.

trans-unit.source: This collection only contains properties that were explicitly requested through <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.PropertiesToLoad%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Den här samlingen innehåller endast egenskaper som begärdes explicit via <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.PropertiesToLoad%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.PropertiesToLoad%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyCollection"></xref> of properties set on this object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyCollection"> </xref> egenskaper som angetts för objektet.
